article.headline: UC Irvine 79, CS Northridge 69
article.story: IRVINE, Calif. -- Adam Folker and Daman Starring scored 14 points apiece as UC Irvine topped Cal State Northridge 79-69 on Saturday. Will Davis II added 13 points, 8 rebounds and 5 blocked shots for UC Irvine (9-9, 3-2 Big West). Michael Wilder and Alex Young had nine assists each for the Anteaters. The Anteaters shot a season-best 63.8 percent from the field and were 11 of 18 from three-point range for 61.1 percent, also a season high. Stephen Maxwell led Cal State Northridge (9-8, 0-5) with 20 points, hitting 9 of 13 shots. Josh Greene scored 15 points and Trevone Williams and Allan Guei each added 11 points.
